<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 27 at 10:18AM EST  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...AREAS OF DENSE FOG POSSIBLE TODAY...
Fog is gradually moving in over the area resulting in visibility
of one quarter to one half of a mile. Motorists should use their
low beam headlights to be seen by other drivers, and be alert for
changing conditions.
If conditions worsen, a dense fog advisory may be needed later on.</description>
